Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋脏于心中的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便存在于相同之时空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或目睹相同之景物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存于你我内心之物\N亦绝非相同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我内心深处的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(无脸男)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:01:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清冷的月光照着你徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话却说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹记那虚伪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却那温暖的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.32,0:01:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什么样的风景？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的下弦月隐脏于云间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述说着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又将对月长叹…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(后篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂能如你所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不愿现出原形…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安份一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么刚刚的戏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.14,0:02:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续演下去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基于人的渊源跟因果形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当妖怪感应到人类的感情或执念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就会变成物怪\N对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说过您是来斩除物怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在就能斩除的话\N我也是十分乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是物怪的真与理…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有若缺少形的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔剑是无法拔出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻烦啊！物怪这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”乃事情的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”乃心的样貌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若物怪不现出他的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我只得请你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细道出真与理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…一生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！拿酒来，酒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没酒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.93,0:04:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨手笨脚的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪里怪气的家伙\N物怪看上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨人厌真讨人厌\N就是你这种情绪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨人厌真讨人厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…对物怪来说\N你非常适合他附身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这确实很可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这可笑之事，你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于物怪力量的下场即是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每天不停仰望的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片只属于你的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我的...天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是...看着它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看着天空\N我就已经觉得很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...不离开这里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正杀死的人...是谁？\N闭...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正...杀死的人？\N闭...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再踏入蝴蝶小姐的内心！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想离开此地的话此地即是牢狱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想留在此地的话此地即是堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里跟那里都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直认为此处是监牢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...为什么不逃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟以前的我\N简直就是一个模子印出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这样美丽的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能嫁入武士之家的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...最喜欢母亲大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了，蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是假的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏正要上演
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二幕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你天生就是个美人\N这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭这个脸蛋再学点技艺的话\N母亲大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是出身贫寒的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能嫁入大户人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~好孩子，真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢母亲大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望让她开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在忍耐吗？\N咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜牺牲自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...心？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说这么多次了你还是不懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿你不是练好几次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次，从头开始\N对不起，对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你怎么嫁入武士之家？\N对不起，对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，再来一遍\N对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了！快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身已将她调教得\N不管何时都不会令家门蒙羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三幕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还请各位多多照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把头抬起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样拼命恳求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会害我过意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会茶道，弹琴跟花道是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚上会像荡妇一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦，那要看大哥怎么调教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼\N女人只要有钱还怕找不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后务必请您多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲的愿望...吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N请各位务必多多照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人很早就过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俸禄也跟着停止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于失去一切的母亲来说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我嫁入武士之家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她的生存意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来\N我就无愧于梅泽家的代代祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就成了\N替母亲实现愿望的工具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然那又是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了母亲的愿望\N而压抑自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但身为工具的你却...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你恋爱的对象...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四幕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早点拿来不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨手笨脚的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪里怪气的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你干嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老妈苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一个媳妇上吊自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会让这种女人进门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过娶来做饭刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多点情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌~你怎么讲这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...别问了...别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再问了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问了...别问了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐那个面具...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是物怪操控那个戴面具的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把你束缚在那个家里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“真“
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而接受了母亲扭曲的爱\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致你的心也跟着扭曲\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是被物怪缠上\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“理“
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...最喜欢母亲大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有认真练习吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能嫁入豪门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...已经很努力了\N我也会引以为傲的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很努力...很努力了\N之后再生个健康的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要我不要...\N为了得到夫家的疼爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要我不要啊...\N你一定要拼个儿子出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人听我说...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待啊~\N母亲大人你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水天宫的符好像很有用呢\N母亲大人听我说...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人你听我说啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让他弟弟抢先的话\N那就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人为什么不听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说听我说啊...\N所以你一定要先生出小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说...\N啊~真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说好不好\N好期待哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N好期待哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直跟白痴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了他人的欲望\N我杀了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记自已面貌的...\N我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪\N杀了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现出...形来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后可以问件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无脸男为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自已得救了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱上你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是个无法实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的...物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢，我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你拿酒来在搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早点拿来不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨手笨脚的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪里怪气的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你干嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老妈苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一个媳妇上吊自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会让这种女人进门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过娶来做饭刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多点情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌~你怎么讲这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你还在干麻啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了...真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错\N实在是怪里怪气的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，蝴蝶\N真讨人厌...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聋啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什么事情都拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点用也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得她在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是怎么教的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶，快把酒拿来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点拿来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒还没好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(完)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.61,0:21:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你不在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法笑得开怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能将那些无可取代的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜并活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛开在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随风缓缓飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不见的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N将是我此生无可比喻的珍爱
